-\frac12\left(z+\frac1z\right)=-\frac12\frac{z^2+1}z\cdot\frac{\overline z}{\overline z}=-\frac12\frac{z|z|^2+\overline z}{|z|^2}=
=-\frac1{2|z|^2}\left(x(|z|^2+1)+y(|z|^2-1)i\right)
